headline: Quarterra Multifamily Announces the Start of Leasing at Cordelia Apartments
summary: Quarterra Multifamily, a subsidiary of Lennar Corporation and a multifamily apartment developer, property manager, and asset manager, today announced the start of leasing at Cordelia, a luxury high-rise community in Downtown Sarasota, Fla., on Sarasota Bay.
